thread.title_full: White, Jacobs & Associates reviewed by Gurpal Singh

author: Gurpal Singh
title: Gurpal Singh
text: Gonzalo Marroquin provided exceptional help in resolving my credit disputes. He was very thorough and answered all my questions in timely manner. They never tried to extend the process like so many other companies do. Above all I will recommend that any body looking for any help with there credit needs to contact these guys.
